      <bcl:subsection id="d1e386">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>For the purposes of this section, the jurisdiction of the City of Vancouver does not include the excluded port lands.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d1e395">
        <bcl:num>3</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>In this section, <in:term>excluded port lands</in:term> means that portion of the lands described in Schedule B, titled "Vancouver Fraser Port Authority Description of Federal Real Property" of the Letters Patent for the Vancouver Fraser Port Authority set out in Order in Council P.C. 2007-1885 included within the boundaries of the City of Vancouver.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 234/2004, s. (b); am. B.C. Regs. 288/2004; 22/2011, s. (c); 245/2018, s. 1.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/03039_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Safety Standards Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, S.B.C. 2003, c. 39, relevant to the enactment of this regulation: sections 84 (1) and 89 (c)]</reg:provisionsnote>
